   Joerg, Lucie, Albany Med Coll, Albany, NY USA.
   Kabakova, Margaret; Wang, Jennifer Y.; Austin, Evan; Cohen, Marc; Kurtti, Alana; Jagdeo, Jared, SUNY Downstate Hlth Sci Univ, Dept Dermatol, Brooklyn, NY USA.
